org.opendaylight.controller.filtervalve.cors.model

Class UrlMatcher<FILTER>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.filtervalve.cors.model.UrlMatcher<FILTER>

  • public class UrlMatcher<FILTER>
extends java.lang.Object
    Match incoming URL with user defined patterns according to servlet specification. In the Web application deployment descriptor, the following syntax is used to define mappings:
    • A string beginning with a ‘/’ character and ending with a ‘/*’ suffix is used for path mapping.
    • A string beginning with a ‘*.’ prefix is used as an extension mapping.
    • All other strings are used for exact matches only.
